highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Golden” is the highest at #1.
“YOGURCITO REMIX (feat. Kris R., ROA)” by Blessd, Anuel AA, Yan Block, Luar La L, Kris R., and ROA is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #193.
“Sweater Weather” by The Neighbourhood has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 1810 days straight.
“cardigan” by Taylor Swift is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 98 spots at #81.
